                            <comment id="12905927" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 3 Sep 2010 14:52:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch applies reversed flag during collation from different data sources and makes QF.getColumnComparator package-private to make it more difficult to make the same mistake again.  unit test added to TableTest.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12905945" author="brandon.williams" created="Fri, 3 Sep 2010 16:05:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1, though maybe the flush in the test should be explicit since it&apos;s not immediately obvious it will occur after 20 ops.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12906319" author="jbellis" created="Sun, 5 Sep 2010 03:31:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed, w/ test adjusted as suggested&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
